Hello everybody....a short description of my new map:
This is the 2. version of the map: gg_150seconds!
I changed 3-4 things!
It´s no longer a "gg_map" - now it´s a fy_map with weapons on the spawn-positions!
In the first version [URL=http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/53939]KLICKHERE[/URL] 
the glass-walls are going down in 150 seconds!
In the new version the glass-wall don´t go down-the wall break after a delay of 120seconds!
This update cause that you also could fall down in the water.
But warning-if you fall down you die for 100%!
And also warning: After 120seconds there isn´t any wall to cover you!

A new "spezial" also is that I've create a 3D-skybox!
And a wall witch borders the map!
Maby -I hope so- you have fun with the v2!

your rhino!

Ps: a small feedback could be nice =)
